title: Support adding extra request-response protocols to the node
doc:
- audience: Node Dev
  description: Allow adding extra request-response protocols during polkadot service
    initialization. This is required to add a request-response protocol described
    in [RFC-0008](https://polkadot-fellows.github.io/RFCs/approved/0008-parachain-bootnodes-dht.html)
    to the relay chain side of the parachain node.
crates:
- name: polkadot-service
  bump: minor
